    SetCurve(Int32, Single, Single, Single, Single)

    Sets the specified key frame to Bezier interpolation. 

    cx1
    and 
    cx2
    are from 0 to 1, representing the percent of time between the two key frames. 
    cy1
    and 
    cy2
    are the percent of the difference between the key frame's values.
